participantgroup #lightgreen #blue:3
  participant "Client1(lower MAC)" as Client1
  participant "Client2(higher MAC)" as Client2
end

box over Client1:Opens socket waiting for specific client
Client1<-Client2: Connects to socket
box over Client1:Check MAC Address
box over Client1:Close socket
Client1-->Client2: Send message "CONN"
Client1<->Client2: Data send